webpackJsonp([0xef5d83677db1],{828:function(e,t){e.exports={data:{markdownRemark:{html:'<h3>What are they?</h3>\n<p>Triggers are simple, but powerful tools for executing automated responses to new, incoming reports. With triggers, you can set up an automated action when your program receives a report with or without a given trigger word. Triggers aid in reducing noise as they can flag certain reports.</p>\n<h3>Default Triggers</h3>\n<p>When you go to Settings > Program > Automation > Triggers, you\'ll notice a list of default triggers that have already been made for your program. You can choose to edit or delete these triggers.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/triggers-5-f54d6b015fc1761cf801ad6a8082eb53-40463.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 35.416666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="triggers-5"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/triggers-5-f54d6b015fc1761cf801ad6a8082eb53-2f183.png"\n        srcset="/static/triggers-5-f54d6b015fc1761cf801ad6a8082eb53-67829.png 125w,\n/static/triggers-5-f54d6b015fc1761cf801ad6a8082eb53-5c59f.png 250w,\n/static/triggers-5-f54d6b015fc1761cf801ad6a8082eb53-2f183.png 500w,\n/static/triggers-5-f54d6b015fc1761cf801ad6a8082eb53-c93e8.png 750w,\n/static/triggers-5-f54d6b015fc1761cf801ad6a8082eb53-4e628.png 1000w,\n/static/triggers-5-f54d6b015fc1761cf801ad6a8082eb53-40463.png 1440w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h3>Adding Triggers</h3>\n<p>To add new triggers:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <strong>Settings > Program > Automation > Triggers</strong>.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Add new Trigger</strong>.\n\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/triggers-1-764be1966d88b62c8baf19f758c2c15b-3fefc.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 39.36899862825789%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="triggers-1"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/triggers-1-764be1966d88b62c8baf19f758c2c15b-2f183.png"\n        srcset="/static/triggers-1-764be1966d88b62c8baf19f758c2c15b-67829.png 125w,\n/static/triggers-1-764be1966d88b62c8baf19f758c2c15b-5c59f.png 250w,\n/static/triggers-1-764be1966d88b62c8baf19f758c2c15b-2f183.png 500w,\n/static/triggers-1-764be1966d88b62c8baf19f758c2c15b-c93e8.png 750w,\n/static/triggers-1-764be1966d88b62c8baf19f758c2c15b-4e628.png 1000w,\n/static/triggers-1-764be1966d88b62c8baf19f758c2c15b-3fefc.png 1458w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </li>\n<li>\n<p>In the first dropdown of the <strong>IF</strong> section, you can choose to have your trigger be within:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Any Field</li>\n<li>Report Title</li>\n<li>Report Body</li>\n<li>Report Weakness</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>In the second dropdown, select whether you want your trigger to be set off when a specific section of the report either <strong>Contains</strong> or <strong>Does not contain</strong> the trigger.</li>\n<li>Enter the trigger word(s) in the <strong>Enter trigger criteria</strong> field. Triggers can range from being a single word or phrase and can also include numbers and symbols.\n\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/triggers-2-bb4cc788f82d8add0544ef58be3b5d7d-daf25.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 35.37234042553192%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="triggers-2"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/triggers-2-bb4cc788f82d8add0544ef58be3b5d7d-2f183.png"\n        srcset="/static/triggers-2-bb4cc788f82d8add0544ef58be3b5d7d-67829.png 125w,\n/static/triggers-2-bb4cc788f82d8add0544ef58be3b5d7d-5c59f.png 250w,\n/static/triggers-2-bb4cc788f82d8add0544ef58be3b5d7d-2f183.png 500w,\n/static/triggers-2-bb4cc788f82d8add0544ef58be3b5d7d-c93e8.png 750w,\n/static/triggers-2-bb4cc788f82d8add0544ef58be3b5d7d-4e628.png 1000w,\n/static/triggers-2-bb4cc788f82d8add0544ef58be3b5d7d-b3ac4.png 1500w,\n/static/triggers-2-bb4cc788f82d8add0544ef58be3b5d7d-daf25.png 1504w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<p><i>Note: The number and list of existing program reports that meet the criteria of your trigger shows.</i></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/triggers-3-dfc5cdf66af9a65ac6ec52577f367ed3-6bd54.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 73.61319340329835%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="triggers-3"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/triggers-3-dfc5cdf66af9a65ac6ec52577f367ed3-2f183.png"\n        srcset="/static/triggers-3-dfc5cdf66af9a65ac6ec52577f367ed3-67829.png 125w,\n/static/triggers-3-dfc5cdf66af9a65ac6ec52577f367ed3-5c59f.png 250w,\n/static/triggers-3-dfc5cdf66af9a65ac6ec52577f367ed3-2f183.png 500w,\n/static/triggers-3-dfc5cdf66af9a65ac6ec52577f367ed3-c93e8.png 750w,\n/static/triggers-3-dfc5cdf66af9a65ac6ec52577f367ed3-4e628.png 1000w,\n/static/triggers-3-dfc5cdf66af9a65ac6ec52577f367ed3-6bd54.png 1334w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<ol start="6">\n<li><em>(Optional)</em> Select <strong>add another rule for this trigger</strong> to add more conditions for your trigger.</li>\n<li>In the <strong>THEN</strong> section, set the action you\'d like your trigger to take. You can choose from: </li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Option</th>\n<th>Detail</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Show warning: Ask for submission confirmation</td>\n<td>Hackers will be asked for submission confirmation</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Add Comment: all participants</td>\n<td>A public comment will be posted on the report</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Change State: Request more information</td>\n<td>The report state will be changed to needs more info</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/triggers-4-e354f07fc30d8d0828fb7bf27deab82e-76291.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 61.66219839142091%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="triggers-4"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/triggers-4-e354f07fc30d8d0828fb7bf27deab82e-2f183.png"\n        srcset="/static/triggers-4-e354f07fc30d8d0828fb7bf27deab82e-67829.png 125w,\n/static/triggers-4-e354f07fc30d8d0828fb7bf27deab82e-5c59f.png 250w,\n/static/triggers-4-e354f07fc30d8d0828fb7bf27deab82e-2f183.png 500w,\n/static/triggers-4-e354f07fc30d8d0828fb7bf27deab82e-c93e8.png 750w,\n/static/triggers-4-e354f07fc30d8d0828fb7bf27deab82e-4e628.png 1000w,\n/static/triggers-4-e354f07fc30d8d0828fb7bf27deab82e-76291.png 1492w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<ol start="8">\n<li>Type the message you want to give to the hacker when the trigger goes off.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Save trigger</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Result</h3>\n<p>Once your trigger is set up, when new, incoming reports meet the criteria of your trigger, the appropriate action will automatically be applied to the report. This will save you time from having to manually respond to every report that comes in. </p>',frontmatter:{path:"/programs/triggers.html",id:"programs/triggers",title:"Triggers",description:null}}},pathContext:{}}}});
